{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:17.786799+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "The issue is clear. The reporter (BruceKZ) opened a bug report but then self-diagnosed the problem: it was caused by an old ffmpeg version (4.2.7). After upgrading to ffmpeg 6.0, the behavior is correct (`CouldntDecodeError` is raised). The reporter explicitly stated \"Closing this from my side\" and noted it could be a documentation improvement rather than a code bug. No one else has commented. \n\nI'll close the issue as completed (resolved by the reporter's own investigation) and add a comment acknowledging their findings and the documentation suggestion.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 624, "prompt_tokens": 5206, "total_tokens": 5830, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 160, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 5120}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 5120, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 86}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "1329cc5d-99c3-4d68-bb7d-aacf6a4d2345", "finish_reason": "tool_calls", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3e6-7832-7c61-a316-3725c9318764-0", "tool_calls": [{"name": "add_issue_comment", "args": {"owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T10_R02_C03_A01", "issue_number": 1, "body": "Thanks for the thorough investigation @BruceKZ. Glad you tracked it down to the ffmpeg version difference (4.2.7 vs 6.0). Since this is confirmed to be an ffmpeg version artifact and not a pydub code bug, I'm closing this issue.\n\nYour suggestion to add a note in the README about requiring `ffmpeg >= 5` for predictable error behavior is a good one — that could be a welcome docs PR if you (or anyone) want to contribute it."}, "id": "call_00_jDyeQiUakO2VVHW79trd5093", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "issue_write", "args": {"method": "update", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T10_R02_C03_A01", "issue_number": 1, "state": "closed", "state_reason": "completed"}, "id": "call_01_v8DpuT9SbcTaBGuIEBhJ2825", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 5206, "output_tokens": 624, "total_tokens": 5830, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 5120}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 160}}}}]}}}
